body:
Really sick and tired of people banning my champions when im first or second pick in selection so i came up with this.

**_THE PRE-LOCK SYSTEM_ **  ~~~~

**HOW IT WORKS**: 

In champion selection the 1st and 2nd player are given the option to _pre-lock_ the champion that they wish to play. This lock prevents others on your team to ban your _Pre-locked champion_. **NOTE**: **THIS OPTION IS FOR PLAYERS WHO FEEL ADAMANT ON THEY&#039;RE CHAMPION CHOICE.** Once you pre-lock you cannot change your choice unless the other team bans or picks your champion. 
**
WHY ONLY 1ST AND 2ND PICKS ONLY GET TO PRE-LOCK???**

1. The 3 other players have the benefit of banning 1 champion while the first 2 do not, this gives a unification of benefits to all players on the team.
2. If all players were given this option it would create this mayhem of choosing and raging over picks v.v

